Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}動不了？ 還是不想動？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}將孤獨轉化為強悍！
