Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和劉鳳的對決中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白於天下
